theorem Topology.closure_eq_closure_interior_union_of_P3
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    Topology.P3 (A := A) → Topology.P3 (A := B) →
      closure (A ∪ B) = closure (interior (A ∪ B)) := by
  intro hA hB
  -- `P3` is stable under unions
  have hUnion : Topology.P3 (A := A ∪ B) :=
    Topology.P3_union (A := A) (B := B) hA hB
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  · -- First inclusion: `closure (A ∪ B) ⊆ closure (interior (A ∪ B))`
    have hSub : (A ∪ B : Set X) ⊆ interior (closure (A ∪ B)) := hUnion
    have hClosSub :
        closure (A ∪ B) ⊆ closure (interior (closure (A ∪ B))) :=
      closure_mono hSub
    -- Rewrite the right‐hand side using a previously proved equality
    have hEq :
        closure (interior (closure (A ∪ B))) =
          closure (interior (A ∪ B)) :=
      Topology.closure_interior_closure_interior_eq_closure_interior
        (X := X) (A := A ∪ B)
    simpa [hEq] using hClosSub
  · -- Second inclusion: monotonicity of `closure`
    exact closure_mono
      (interior_subset : interior (A ∪ B) ⊆ A ∪ B)

theorem Topology.interior_inter_of_isOpen_right {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A B : Set X} (hB : IsOpen B) :
    interior (A ∩ B) = interior A ∩ B := by
  ext x
  constructor
  · intro hx
    rcases mem_interior.mp hx with ⟨U, hU_open, hxU, hU_sub⟩
    have hU_subA : U ⊆ A := fun y hyU => (hU_sub hyU).1
    have hx_intA : x ∈ interior A :=
      mem_interior.mpr ⟨U, hU_open, hxU, hU_subA⟩
    have hx_B : x ∈ B := (hU_sub hxU).2
    exact And.intro hx_intA hx_B
  · rintro ⟨hx_intA, hxB⟩
    rcases mem_interior.mp hx_intA with ⟨U, hU_open, hxU, hU_subA⟩
    have hxU' : x ∈ U ∩ B := And.intro hxU hxB
    have hUV_open : IsOpen (U ∩ B) := isOpen_inter hU_open hB
    have hUV_sub : (U ∩ B : Set X) ⊆ A ∩ B := fun y hy =>
      And.intro (hU_subA hy.1) hy.2
    exact mem_interior.mpr ⟨U ∩ B, hUV_open, hxU', hUV_sub⟩

theorem Topology.isClosed_closure_interior {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    IsClosed (closure (interior A)) := by
  simpa using isClosed_closure (s := interior A)
